imdb.plot outline: Corazón Valiente (Fearless Heart), originally known as Caídas del Cielo, is a Spanish-language telenovela produced by United States-based television network Telemundo Studios, Miami, featuring an ensemble cast. Adriana Fonseca, Ximena Duque, José Luis Reséndez and Fabián Ríos starred as the main protagonists, with Aylin Mujica and Manuel Landeta starred as the main antagonists.
imdb.title: Fearless Heart
plot: Corazón Valiente (_Fearless Heart_ (qv)), originally known as Caídas del Cielo, is a Spanish-language telenovela produced by United States-based television network Telemundo Studios, Miami, featuring an ensemble cast. Adriana Fonseca, Ximena Duque, José Luis Reséndez and Fabián Ríos starred as the main protagonists, with Aylin Mujica and Manuel Landeta starred as the main antagonists.::Drehluta Naomi Andreea
